  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 13.3,
      "text": "Screen English"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.3,
      "end": 34.78,
      "text": "To enjoy a movie, Screen English Time"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.78,
      "end": 38.48,
      "text": "5월에 함께하고 있는 영화는 The Peanut Butter Falcon"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.48,
      "end": 41.8,
      "text": "It's a movie about a young man with down syndrome"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.8,
      "end": 44.86,
      "text": "who runs away from a nursing home."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.94,
      "end": 47.36,
      "text": "Oh, thanks for the brief explanation."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.9,
      "end": 48.52,
      "text": "My pleasure."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.04,
      "end": 50.8,
      "text": "아우, 속이 아주 편안하네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 51.06,
      "end": 53.74,
      "text": "네, 그리스 씨가 이렇게 설명을 잘 해주시니까는"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.74,
      "end": 55.06,
      "text": "Oh, I'm glad to hear that."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.08,
      "end": 55.34,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.54,
      "end": 55.98,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.98,
      "end": 58.88,
      "text": "아우, 자, 우리가 yesterday, 어저께요,"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.0,
      "end": 60.92,
      "text": "we had to talk about Zach, 그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.12,
      "end": 62.14,
      "text": "Yes, Zach."
    },
    {
      "start": 62.56,
      "end": 63.18,
      "text": "Last name."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.32,
      "end": 64.2,
      "text": "Last name, 포기했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.2,
      "end": 65.36,
      "text": "생략이, 포기, 바이바이."
    },
    {
      "start": 65.6,
      "end": 66.82,
      "text": "네, 생략했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.82,
      "end": 69.16,
      "text": "Zach Potsegan, 갓스겐, 저도 못해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.62,
      "end": 70.22,
      "text": "갓스겐."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.42,
      "end": 74.0,
      "text": "Zach Gatsugan이라는 인물에 대해서 이야기를 나눠봤었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.0,
      "end": 77.0,
      "text": "Still, I need some more information about him."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.3,
      "end": 78.34,
      "text": "Zach Gatsugan."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.62,
      "end": 81.0,
      "text": "So, he's a little older than me."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.12,
      "end": 82.84,
      "text": "He was born in 1985."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.62,
      "end": 86.22,
      "text": "So, in his mid to late thirties."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.44,
      "end": 87.34,
      "text": "Late thirties."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.42,
      "end": 88.12,
      "text": "Late thirties."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.18,
      "end": 88.4,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.94,
      "end": 91.84,
      "text": "And his original name was, his full name,"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.3,
      "end": 95.1,
      "text": "Zachary Robin Gatsugan."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.1,
      "end": 96.04,
      "text": "한번 해볼래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.04,
      "end": 99.44,
      "text": "Zachary Robin Gatsugan."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.64,
      "end": 100.06,
      "text": "Oh, good."
    },
    {
      "start": 100.2,
      "end": 100.66,
      "text": "괜찮아요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.68,
      "end": 100.94,
      "text": "Perfect."
    },
    {
      "start": 101.44,
      "end": 102.04,
      "text": "긴장했잖아요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.32,
      "end": 103.78,
      "text": "First name, middle name, last name."
    },
    {
      "start": 103.78,
      "end": 104.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.14,
      "end": 104.6,
      "text": "Very good."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.76,
      "end": 107.6,
      "text": "들어보니까, 그러면 이 타일러 역을 맡았던"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.6,
      "end": 111.84,
      "text": "Shaya Leboeuf, 이 사람은 1986년생이니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.84,
      "end": 114.84,
      "text": "나이를 따지자면 이 Zach가 한 살 위이네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.92,
      "end": 115.64,
      "text": "한 살 형이네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.72,
      "end": 116.22,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 116.22,
      "end": 116.56,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 116.82,
      "end": 117.3,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.3,
      "end": 117.7,
      "text": "Interesting."
    },
    {
      "start": 118.16,
      "end": 118.5,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 118.74,
      "end": 121.74,
      "text": "But they are very similar in age."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.74,
      "end": 126.28,
      "text": "And one thing special about him is recently,"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.48,
      "end": 130.36,
      "text": "he was at the Academy Awards last year."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.48,
      "end": 131.18,
      "text": "Last year."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.32,
      "end": 134.24,
      "text": "When Gi Seng Chung won the best picture."
    },
    {
      "start": 134.44,
      "end": 135.6,
      "text": "Oh, I'm so proud of it."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.64,
      "end": 137.44,
      "text": "He was there on February 9th, 2020."
    },
    {
      "start": 137.44,
      "end": 144.3,
      "text": "And he made Academy Awards history by becoming the first person with Down Syndrome to present"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.3,
      "end": 145.22,
      "text": "an award."
    },
    {
      "start": 145.22,
      "end": 152.78,
      "text": "So he presented the best live action short film at the Oscars with his co-star Shaya Leboeuf."
    },
    {
      "start": 152.92,
      "end": 155.76,
      "text": "They were there together presenting the award on stage."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.76,
      "end": 157.0,
      "text": "And he made history."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.24,
      "end": 158.38,
      "text": "와, 그렇군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 158.64,
      "end": 160.38,
      "text": "이 공동주연이었잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 161.32,
      "end": 163.06,
      "text": "이 Shaya Leboeuf."
    },
    {
      "start": 163.18,
      "end": 163.62,
      "text": "Shaya."
    },
    {
      "start": 163.66,
      "end": 164.98,
      "text": "Yeah, Shaya Leboeuf."
    },
    {
      "start": 165.14,
      "end": 165.58,
      "text": "Leboeuf."
    },
    {
      "start": 165.74,
      "end": 166.2,
      "text": "몸짱."
    },
    {
      "start": 166.5,
      "end": 166.68,
      "text": "Shaya."
    },
    {
      "start": 166.68,
      "end": 171.32,
      "text": "아니, 성을 신경 썼더니 first name이 헷갈리고 아주 난리가 났네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 171.5,
      "end": 172.72,
      "text": "이거 흔한 이름 아니에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 172.8,
      "end": 173.3,
      "text": "아, 그렇군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 173.3,
      "end": 173.88,
      "text": "이분 이름은."
    },
    {
      "start": 173.9,
      "end": 174.44,
      "text": "고마워요."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.56,
      "end": 175.58,
      "text": "그렇게 이야기해 주셔서."
    },
    {
      "start": 175.58,
      "end": 182.1,
      "text": "네, 아무튼 이분하고 같이 작년에 오스카상에서 단편 영화상을"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.1,
      "end": 187.48,
      "text": "심지어 다운 징후군 배우로서 최초로 수상을 하는 영예를 얻게 됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.82,
      "end": 190.78,
      "text": "그래서 그 기립박수를 받았다고 들었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.92,
      "end": 192.32,
      "text": "기립박수 영어로 뭐게요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.5,
      "end": 193.18,
      "text": "뭘까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.3,
      "end": 193.88,
      "text": "뭘까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.28,
      "end": 197.34,
      "text": "스탠딩 오베이션?"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.44,
      "end": 198.14,
      "text": "Is that right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.24,
      "end": 199.1,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 199.12,
      "end": 199.78,
      "text": "Thanks a lot."
    },
    {
      "start": 199.86,
      "end": 201.22,
      "text": "He received the standing ovation."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.22,
      "end": 207.86,
      "text": "이야, 진짜 저도 이 장면을 보고 있었더라면 집에서라도 기립박수 쳤을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.9,
      "end": 211.67,
      "text": "자, 오늘 장면 먼저 확인해 보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 211.67,
      "end": 212.87,
      "text": "Okay, you're a lot of jokes."
    },
    {
      "start": 213.69,
      "end": 215.19,
      "text": "I'm looking for a missing person."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.39,
      "end": 219.33,
      "text": "Have either of you gentlemen, I'm assuming I can use the word gentleman."
    },
    {
      "start": 219.79,
      "end": 220.25,
      "text": "Have you seen him?"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.29,
      "end": 222.35,
      "text": "No, I ain't seen him."
    },
    {
      "start": 222.85,
      "end": 223.57,
      "text": "Have you seen him?"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.23,
      "end": 224.83,
      "text": "Well, what do you do?"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.51,
      "end": 227.57,
      "text": "He ran away from the nursing home I work at."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.57,
      "end": 233.29,
      "text": "Finally, Tyler하고 Zach가 met together 했었잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 233.45,
      "end": 234.15,
      "text": "They did meet."
    },
    {
      "start": 234.39,
      "end": 237.49,
      "text": "근데 어떻게 만났던지 혹시 기억나십니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.59,
      "end": 239.87,
      "text": "It was not under the best circumstances."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.87,
      "end": 242.47,
      "text": "Very bad circumstances."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.75,
      "end": 243.11,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.19,
      "end": 248.21,
      "text": "오늘 보트였는데 아주 그냥 관건이었던 장면이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.37,
      "end": 249.57,
      "text": "They were both running away."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.71,
      "end": 251.39,
      "text": "They're still both running away."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.97,
      "end": 254.29,
      "text": "Zach is running away from a retirement home."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.29,
      "end": 259.31,
      "text": "And Tyler is running from these crazy guys who want to hurt him."
    },
    {
      "start": 259.37,
      "end": 259.81,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 260.07,
      "end": 262.37,
      "text": "Duncan하고 그의 일동이었죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 262.45,
      "end": 262.81,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.61,
      "end": 267.67,
      "text": "So, Duncan하고 그 측근들이 그러면 are they Tyler's rivals?"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.67,
      "end": 269.49,
      "text": "I don't know about rivals."
    },
    {
      "start": 269.87,
      "end": 270.91,
      "text": "They hate Tyler."
    },
    {
      "start": 271.63,
      "end": 275.99,
      "text": "Tyler was fishing illegally in that special part of the water."
    },
    {
      "start": 276.59,
      "end": 279.33,
      "text": "And they had the license for that fishing."
    },
    {
      "start": 279.57,
      "end": 282.11,
      "text": "근데 라이선스는 타일러의 형 거였는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.13,
      "end": 282.71,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.73,
      "end": 284.67,
      "text": "참 말이 안 되는 그런 상황이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 284.75,
      "end": 285.67,
      "text": "It should go to Tyler."
    },
    {
      "start": 285.87,
      "end": 289.15,
      "text": "But 무슨 우리도 모르는 사연이 있었나 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 289.15,
      "end": 292.13,
      "text": "아무튼 이 던큰이라는 사람들 마음에 안 들어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.53,
      "end": 292.75,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.77,
      "end": 295.25,
      "text": "Anyway, he, Zach doesn't like them either."
    },
    {
      "start": 295.37,
      "end": 297.27,
      "text": "Or Tyler doesn't like them either."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.39,
      "end": 299.89,
      "text": "He burned their gear."
    },
    {
      "start": 300.11,
      "end": 301.03,
      "text": "Did you see that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.19,
      "end": 302.81,
      "text": "정말 깜짝 놀랐어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.81,
      "end": 303.73,
      "text": "He burned it."
    },
    {
      "start": 303.93,
      "end": 308.19,
      "text": "And now he's running away in a boat and by foot."
    },
    {
      "start": 308.41,
      "end": 310.31,
      "text": "Just trying to get away as far as he can."
    },
    {
      "start": 311.01,
      "end": 313.57,
      "text": "그리고 나서 어저께 엘리너가요."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.79,
      "end": 315.19,
      "text": "Was in a difficult situation."
    },
    {
      "start": 315.61,
      "end": 319.25,
      "text": "So, she had to start looking for Zach."
    },
    {
      "start": 319.61,
      "end": 319.87,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 319.97,
      "end": 322.73,
      "text": "She needs to find Zach who is missing ASAP."
    },
    {
      "start": 322.95,
      "end": 323.23,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 323.37,
      "end": 325.39,
      "text": "Otherwise, they're going to report this to the state."
    },
    {
      "start": 325.39,
      "end": 329.31,
      "text": "And the retirement home is going to be under investigation."
    },
    {
      "start": 329.73,
      "end": 330.09,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.15,
      "end": 331.01,
      "text": "거치가 아플 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 331.13,
      "end": 331.59,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 331.59,
      "end": 334.81,
      "text": "그래서 she's just dropped by the small shop."
    },
    {
      "start": 335.39,
      "end": 335.63,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.81,
      "end": 336.01,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 336.07,
      "end": 337.69,
      "text": "It's like a little convenience store."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.85,
      "end": 338.83,
      "text": "I see."
    },
    {
      "start": 338.93,
      "end": 339.63,
      "text": "Supply store."
    },
    {
      "start": 339.73,
      "end": 339.83,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 339.89,
      "end": 343.95,
      "text": "거기에서 이 Tyler를 마주치면서 대화를 하는 장면을 들으신 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.07,
      "end": 345.83,
      "text": "And Tyler kind of likes her."
    },
    {
      "start": 345.91,
      "end": 346.35,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 346.35,
      "end": 347.57,
      "text": "He starts flirting with her."
    },
    {
      "start": 347.57,
      "end": 348.67,
      "text": "He's crushing her."
    },
    {
      "start": 348.81,
      "end": 349.51,
      "text": "Right away."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.55,
      "end": 349.85,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 349.87,
      "end": 350.65,
      "text": "보자마자."
    },
    {
      "start": 350.67,
      "end": 350.93,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 351.15,
      "end": 352.03,
      "text": "한 눈에 뿅!"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.43,
      "end": 353.57,
      "text": "작업 멘트 바로 들어가요."
    },
    {
      "start": 353.57,
      "end": 356.71,
      "text": "근데 그 작업하는 방식이 영 서툴긴 했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.85,
      "end": 357.11,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.39,
      "end": 359.17,
      "text": "And she's not impressed."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.01,
      "end": 361.45,
      "text": "자, 어떤 표현들이 있었나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 361.59,
      "end": 362.93,
      "text": "Missing person."
    },
    {
      "start": 363.01,
      "end": 364.25,
      "text": "Missing person."
    },
    {
      "start": 364.59,
      "end": 366.45,
      "text": "실종자라는 해석이 되겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 367.27,
      "end": 367.83,
      "text": "Assuming."
